name: Agness Walewinder
description: Agness Walewinder is the co-founder of popular adventure travel blog eTramping and fitness website Run Agness Run. She has been traveling for nine years, working as a digital nomad and online entrepreneur. Originally from Poland, she has a master’s degree in New Media from Amsterdam University, studied English and Spanish for four years at the University of Wolverhampton, and has currently visited 65 countries and counting.
